snippet.title: Geek Gaming Scenics
snippet.description:
Welcome to our YouTube channel dedicated to model terrain building and showcasing the best of Geek Gaming Scenics products! 

Our channel is all about sharing our love of miniature terrain building with the wider community. Whether you're a seasoned hobbyist or just starting out, we hope to inspire you with our tutorials and reviews. Our videos cover a range of topics, from basic terrain building techniques to advanced modelling methods.

In addition to showcasing our terrain creations, we are proud to offer a selection of high-quality Geek Gaming Scenics products and we are excited to share them with our viewers. 

Thank you for joining us on our terrain-building journey, and we hope you enjoy our videos as much as we enjoy creating them. Don't forget to like and subscribe to stay up-to-date with our latest content, and feel free to leave us a comment or message with any questions or suggestions.

snippet.title: BusttheNet Gaming
snippet.description:
Hi there, my name is Daljit, apart from being a content creator, I am also a moderator on the SI forums helping people out with the training and tactics side of the game. 

On this channel you will find guides for Football Manager that cover: Training, Tips and Tricks, Tactics.  You will also find me releasing written guides for the game each year for every new game that is released. I also release views, schedules, shortlists.

The best place to start if you are new to the game is the 101 of Mastering Football Manager, which covers guides that are done in conjunction with the creators of the game Sports Interactive. Other saves include - Gamechanger -  a series of shows that cover FM20, FM21 where I take a look at your saves and offer suggestions. 

This year I livestream on Mondays, Weds and Fridays (1830hrs Singapore)  covering Road to Glory challenges with Forest, Kasimpasa, Sporting Portugal and Dundee United.  I also upload two guide videos each week. 

WV0Q0Z

snippet.title: The Vaniverse Gaming
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Vaniverse Gaming Channel. If you enjoy All things RPG, than you have come to the right place!  My channel focuses on Reviews, Guides, and Gameplay of RPGs both AAA and indie. My goal is to give my viewers information about a game so they can decided if it is something they want to play. I am a huge fan of Dungeons and Dragons (D&D) so a lot of my content is focused on games that are similar to D&D. 

The main thing that sets me a part from other channels is I respond to all comments left on my channel. It may take a bit, but I love hearing from my viewers and look forward to the comments each and every day.
